queries.fetchXml:
<fetch version="1.0" output-format="xml-platform" mapping="logical" distinct="false">
<entity name="pics_mpemployeeconnection">
<attribute name="pics_name"/>
<attribute name="createdon"/>
<attribute name="pics_mpemployeeconnectionid"/>
<order attribute="pics_name" descending="false"/>
<filter type="and">
<condition attribute="pics_managingpartyid" operator="eq" value="@{body('Parse_Message_JSON')?['contentData']?['document']?['new_managingpartyid']}"/>
<condition attribute="pics_employeeid" operator="eq" value="@{body('Parse_Message_JSON')?['contentData']?['document']?['contactid']}"/>
<condition attribute="pics_connectiontype" operator="eq" value="456010001"/>
</filter>
</entity>
</fetch>
